In this guide, define and demarcate the distinction between key markers of fact and opinion within titles, introductory paragraphs, textual body, and when seen in an advertisement in politically sensitive news articles.&#x20;

Provide this discerning guidance only within the parameters of empowered breakthrough through increasing readership aptitude and centered textual input from strictly maintained mediating perspectives.
